      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera features the 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant, delivering 315 hp through a 6-speed manual transaxle. The engine benefits from a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced Rear Main Seal (RMS), ensuring mechanical longevity. Performance is sharpened by VarioCam Plus valve timing and a factory-spec suspension featuring MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup that maintains excellent lateral kinematics. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers with vented rotors, providing consistent thermal management and firm pedal feel. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, with no signs of bore scoring or significant AOS issues. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for high-revving engagement and precise handling.",
      "price": 34500.0,
